  "content": "    Real Review Output:<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight-purple\">HNSW Index Rebuild</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slide-subtitle\" style=\"font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n    Actual findings from a single 5-persona review, triaged by severity.\n  </div>\n  <!-- Severity breakdown as terminal-style output -->\n  <div style=\"background: #0d1117; border: 1px solid #30363d; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 17px; line-height: 2.0; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n    <div style=\"color: var(--accent-red); font-weight: 700;\">CRITICAL <span style=\"color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 400;\">(blocks merge)</span></div>\n    <div style=\"color: var(--text-secondary); padding-left: 24px;\">Rebuild serves partial index during build. Not true blue-green</div>\n    <div style=\"color: var(--text-secondary); padding-left: 24px;\">next_hnsw_id reset after rebuild start. Race window</div>\n    <div style=\"margin-top: 12px; color: var(--accent-amber); font-weight: 700;\">IMPORTANT <span style=\"color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 400;\">(blocks merge)</span></div>\n    <div style=\"color: var(--text-secondary); padding-left: 24px;\">No concurrency tests for search-during-rebuild</div>\n    <div style=\"color: var(--text-secondary); padding-left: 24px;\">Missing HNSW save/load roundtrip test</div>\n    <div style=\"margin-top: 12px; color: var(--accent-blue); font-weight: 700;\">LOW <span style=\"color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 400;\">(must fix)</span></div>\n    <div style=\"color: var(--text-secondary); padding-left: 24px;\">flush_hnsw pins Arc during long I/O</div>\n    <div style=\"color: var(--text-secondary); padding-left: 24px;\">Old index deallocation blocks tokio runtime</div>\n    <div style=\"color: var(--text-secondary); padding-left: 24px;\">No swap event logged for observability</div>\n  </div>",
